       Tarantulas chuckles agian as he hears the heavy thuds agianst the 
shields. "Keep it coming!" He says, and sends out 9 cluster missles at the 
jets while the autoguns, from behinde the shields, continue to assult the 
Bots.

       Klash looks at the scanners and sees Drillbits forces trying to 
penetrate the underside of the island. "Ill drop the blast-boxes. It should 
take care of them." She said.
       The blast-boxes were square aquatic mines that droped from a 
suspension and blew arpat at a diamiter of 25 feet. It was really meant to 
clear away under water debris, but it could do a fairly good amount of damage 
to a ship or kill a bot altogether.

       Hell Beast leaked mechfluid. It as time to leave. With so many 
Predacon forces out and about, the oppertunities were fantastic. "Predacons, 
back to base!" He ordered and they quickly deaprted the battle scene to 
invade another bots fortress and to defend thier own.

       Craken and Bezerker were still outside the Allience Island. "Come, 
they have enough problems and it looks like Zardus' little world it falling 
apart. We have a base to defend." Both departed for the base.
